1 ************************************************************************
2 *
3 * Routines for the computation of the O(as^2) NC massive coefficient
4 * functions.
5 *
6 * These routines are taken from the OPENQCDRAD code by S. Alekhin
7 * included in the xFitter program.
8 *
9 ************************************************************************
10 c These are the functions that give the asymptotic dependence of the
11 c coefficient functions with the appropriate factors. xi = mq2/m2
12 c (Q^2/m2) Longitudinal: equation (19) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
13  double precision function asymp_l(xi)
14  implicit none
15 C=======================================================================
16  double precision pi
17  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
18  double precision tr,cf,ca
19  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
20 C=======================================================================
21  double precision xi, term1, fii_hq, fjj_hq
22  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
23  asymp_l = 1d0/6d0/pi*(4d0/xi - 4d0/3d0*term1
24  1 + (1d0 - 2d0/xi - 1d0/6d0*term1)*fjj_hq(xi)
25  1 - (3d0/xi + 0.25d0*term1)*fii_hq(xi))
26  return
27  end
28 c transverse: equation (20) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
29  double precision function asymp_t(xi)
30  implicit none
31 C=======================================================================
32  double precision pi
33  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
34  double precision tr,cf,ca
35  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
36 C=======================================================================
37  double precision xi, term1, fii_hq, fjj_hq
38  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
39  asymp_t = 1d0/6d0/pi*(-2d0/3d0/xi + 4d0/3d0*term1
40  1 + (7d0/6d0 + 1d0/3d0/xi + 1d0/6d0*term1)*fjj_hq(xi)
41  1 + (1d0 + 2d0/xi + 0.25d0*term1)*fii_hq(xi))
42  return
43  end
44 c longitudinal mass factorization: equation (21) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
45  double precision function asympbar_l(xi)
46  implicit none
47 C=======================================================================
48  double precision pi
49  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
50  double precision tr,cf,ca
51  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
52 C=======================================================================
53  double precision xi, term1, fjj_hq
54  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
55  asympbar_l = 1d0/6d0/pi*(-6d0/xi + 0.5d0*term1
56  1 + (3d0/xi + 0.25d0*term1)*fjj_hq(xi))
57  return
58  end
59 c transverse mass factorization: equation (22) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
60  double precision function asympbar_t(xi)
61  implicit none
62 C=======================================================================
63  double precision pi
64  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
65  double precision tr,cf,ca
66  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
67 C=======================================================================
68  double precision xi, term1, fjj_hq
69  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
70  asympbar_t = 1d0/6d0/pi*(4d0/xi - 0.5d0*term1
71  1 - (1d0 + 2d0/xi + 0.25d0*term1)*fjj_hq(xi))
72  return
73  end
74 c equation (24) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
75  double precision function fii_hq(xi)
76  implicit none
77 C=======================================================================
78  double precision pi
79  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
80  double precision tr,cf,ca
81  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
82 C=======================================================================
83  double precision term1, term2, xi, dilog2
84  term1 = dsqrt(xi)
85  term2 = dsqrt(4d0 + xi)
86  fii_hq = 4d0/term1/term2*(-pi*pi/6d0
87  1 - 0.5d0*(dlog((term2 + term1)/(term2 - term1)))**2
88  1 + (dlog(0.5d0*(1d0 - term1/term2)))**2
89  1 + 2d0*dilog2(0.5d0*(1d0 - term1/term2)))
90  return
91  end
92 c equation (23) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
93  double precision function fjj_hq(xi)
94  implicit none
95  double precision xi, term1, term2
96  term1 = dsqrt(xi)
97  term2 = dsqrt(4d0 + xi)
98  fjj_hq = 4d0/term1/term2*dlog((term2 + term1)/(term2 - term1))
99  return
100  end

102 c This gives the transverse Born coefficient as shown in fig 6a of
103 c NPB392 (1993) 162 - 229. For QCD take TR = 1d0/2d0, for QED take
104 c TR = 1d0
105 c eta = (s - 4d0*m2)/4d0/m2, s is the gamma* gluon (gamma) CM Energy
106 c xi = Q^2/m2
107  double precision function ctg(eta,xi)
108  implicit none
109 C=======================================================================
110  double precision pi
111  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
112  double precision tr,cf,ca
113  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
114 C=======================================================================
115  double precision eta,xi
116  ctg = 0.5d0*pi*tr*(1d0 + eta + 0.25d0*xi)**(-3)*
117  1 (-2d0*((1d0 + eta - 0.25d0*xi)**2 + eta + 1d0)*
118  1 dsqrt(eta/(1d0 + eta)) + (2d0*(1d0 + eta)**2 +
119  1 0.125d0*xi**2 + 2d0*eta + 1d0)*
120  1 dlog((dsqrt(1d0 + eta) + dsqrt(eta))/
121  1 (dsqrt(1d0 + eta) - dsqrt(eta))))
122  return
123  end
124 
125 c Longitudinal coefficient function, see above for additional comments
126 c Fig 6b of NPB392(1993) 162 - 229.
127  double precision function cllog(eta,xi)
128  implicit none
129 C=======================================================================
130  double precision pi
131  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
132  double precision tr,cf,ca
133  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
134 C=======================================================================
135  double precision eta,xi
136  cllog = 0.5d0*pi*tr*xi*(1d0 + eta + 0.25d0*xi)**(-3d0)*
137  1 (2d0*dsqrt(eta*(1d0 + eta)) -
138  1 dlog((dsqrt(1d0 + eta) + dsqrt(eta))/
139  1 (dsqrt(1d0 + eta) - dsqrt(eta))))
140  return
141  end

313 c---------------------
314  double precision function clnlog(eta,xi)
315  implicit none
316 C=======================================================================
317  double precision pi
318  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
319  double precision tr,cf,ca
320  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
321 C=======================================================================
322  double precision eta,xi,beta,rho,cla,clf
323  double precision asymp_l,thresha_l,threshf_l
324 
325  beta=sqrt(eta/(1d0+eta))
326  rho=1d0/(1d0+eta)
327 
328  call sclca(eta,xi,cla)
329  cla=ca*tr*(cla + beta*asymp_l(xi) + rho*thresha_l(eta,xi))
330 
331  call sclcf(eta,xi,clf)
332  clf=cf*tr*(clf + rho*threshf_l(eta,xi))
333 
334  clnlog=cla+clf
335  return
336  end
337 c---------------------

408  double precision function dilog2(x)
409  implicit double precision (a-z)
410  dimension b(8)
411  integer ncall
412  data ncall/0/,pi6/1.644934066848226d+00/,een,vier/1.d+00,.25d+00/
413  ncall = 0
414  if(ncall.eq.0)go to 2
415  1 if(x.lt.0)go to 3
416  if(x.gt.0.5)go to 4
417  z=-dlog(1.-x)
418  7 z2=z*z
419  dilog2=z*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*b(8)+b(7))+b(6))
420  1 +b(5))+b(4))+b(3))+b(2))+een)-z2*vier
421  if(x.gt.een)dilog2=-dilog2-.5*u*u+2.*pi6
422  return
423  2 b(1)=een
424  b(2)=een/36.
425  b(3)=-een/3600.
426  b(4)=een/211680.
427  b(5)=-een/(30.*362880.d+00)
428  b(6)=5./(66.*39916800.d+00)
429  b(7)=-691./(2730.*39916800.d+00*156.)
430  b(8)=een/(39916800.d+00*28080.)
431  ncall=1
432  go to 1
433  3 if(x.gt.-een)go to 5
434  y=een/(een-x)
435  z=-dlog(een-y)
436  z2=z*z
437  u=dlog(y)
438  dilog2=z*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*b(8)+b(7))+b(6))
439  1 +b(5))+b(4))+b(3))+b(2))+een)-z2*vier-u*(z+.5*u)-pi6
440  return
441  4 if(x.ge.een)go to 10
442  y=een-x
443  z=-dlog(x)
444  6 u=dlog(y)
445  z2=z*z
446  dilog2=-z*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*b(8)+b(7))+b(6))
447  1 +b(5))+b(4))+b(3))+b(2))+een-u)+z2*vier+pi6
448  if(x.gt.een)dilog2=-dilog2-.5*z*z+pi6*2.
449  return
450  5 y=een/(een-x)
451  z=-dlog(y)
452  z2=z*z
453  dilog2=-z*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*(z2*b(8)+b(7))+b(6))
454  1 +b(5))+b(4))+b(3))+b(2))+een)-z2*vier
455  return
456  10 if(x.eq.een)go to 20
457  xx=1./x
458  if(x.gt.2.)go to 11
459  z=dlog(x)
460  y=1.-xx
461  go to 6
462  11 u=dlog(x)
463  z=-dlog(1.-xx)
464  go to 7
465  20 dilog2=pi6
466  return
467  end
468 c routine taken out of Numerical Recipes
469  subroutine locate_nr(xx,n,x,j)
470  Integer j,n
471  Double Precision x,xx(n)
472  Integer jl,ju,jm
473  jl = 0
474  ju = n+1
475  10 If (ju - jl .gt. 1) then
476  jm = (ju + jl)/2
477  If ((xx(n) .gt. xx(1)) .eqv. (x .gt. xx(jm))) then
478  jl = jm
479  else
480  ju = jm
481  endif
482  goto 10
483  endif
484  j = jl
485  return
486  End

3172  dleta = dlog10(eta)
3173  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
3174  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
3175  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
3176  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
3177  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
3178  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
3179  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
3180 c interpolating between the appropriate points
3181  delxi = 1d0/6d0
3182  deleta = 1d0/6d0
3183 c lagrange 3-pt.
3184  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
3185  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
3186  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
3187  if (ixi .ge. 72) ieta = 72
3188  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
3189  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
3190  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
3191  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
3192  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
3193  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
3194  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
3195  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
3196  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
3197  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
3198  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
3199  xsclba = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
3200  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
3201  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
3202  return
3203  end

4077  dleta = dlog10(eta)
4078  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
4079  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
4080  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
4081  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
4082  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
4083  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
4084  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
4085 c interpolating between the appropriate points
4086  delxi = 1d0/6d0
4087  deleta = 1d0/6d0
4088 c lagrange 3-pt.
4089  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
4090  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
4091  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
4092  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
4093  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
4094  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
4095  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
4096  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
4097  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
4098  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
4099  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
4100  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
4101  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
4102  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
4103  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
4104  xsclca = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
4105  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
4106  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
4107  return
4108  end

4982  dleta = dlog10(eta)
4983  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
4984  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
4985  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
4986  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
4987  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
4988  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
4989  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
4990 c interpolating between the appropriate points
4991  delxi = 1d0/6d0
4992  deleta = 1d0/6d0
4993 c lagrange 3-pt.
4994  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
4995  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
4996  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
4997  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
4998  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
4999  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
5000  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
5001  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
5002  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
5003  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
5004  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
5005  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
5006  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
5007  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
5008  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
5009  xsclcf = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
5010  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
5011  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
5012  return
5013  end

5898 c lagrange 3-pt.
5899  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
5900  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
5901  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
5902  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
5903  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
5904  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
5905  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
5906  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
5907  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
5908  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
5909  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
5910  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
5911  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
5912  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
5913  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
5914  xsclql = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
5915  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
5916  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
5917  return
5918  end

6792  dleta = dlog10(eta)
6793  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
6794  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
6795  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
6796  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
6797  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
6798  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
6799  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
6800 c interpolating between the appropriate points
6801  delxi = 1d0/6d0
6802  deleta = 1d0/6d0
6803 c lagrange 3-pt.
6804  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
6805  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
6806  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
6807  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
6808  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
6809  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
6810  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
6811  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
6812  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
6813  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
6814  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
6815  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
6816  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
6817  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
6818  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
6819  xsclqt = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
6820  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
6821  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
6822  return
6823  end

7697  dleta = dlog10(eta)
7698  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
7699  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
7700  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
7701  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
7702  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
7703  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
7704  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
7705 c interpolating between the appropriate points
7706  delxi = 1d0/6d0
7707  deleta = 1d0/6d0
7708 c lagrange 3-pt.
7709  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
7710  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
7711  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
7712  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
7713  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
7714  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
7715  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
7716  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
7717  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
7718  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
7719  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
7720  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
7721  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
7722  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
7723  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
7724  xsqlba = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
7725  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
7726  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
7727  return
7728  end

8601 
8602  dleta = dlog10(eta)
8603  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
8604  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
8605  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
8606  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
8607  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
8608  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
8609  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
8610 c interpolating between the appropriate points
8611  delxi = 1d0/6d0
8612  deleta = 1d0/6d0
8613 c lagrange 3-pt.
8614  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
8615  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
8616  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
8617  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
8618  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
8619  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
8620  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
8621  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
8622  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
8623  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
8624  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
8625  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
8626  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
8627  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
8628  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
8629  xsqtba = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
8630  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
8631  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
8632  return
8633  end

9507  dleta = dlog10(eta)
9508  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
9509  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
9510  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
9511  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
9512  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
9513  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
9514  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
9515 c interpolating between the appropriate points
9516  delxi = 1d0/6d0
9517  deleta = 1d0/6d0
9518 c lagrange 3-pt.
9519  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
9520  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
9521  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
9522  if (ixi .ge. 72) ieta = 72
9523  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
9524  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
9525  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
9526  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
9527  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
9528  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
9529  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
9530  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
9531  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
9532  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
9533  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
9534  xsctba = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
9535  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
9536  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
9537  return
9538  end

10422  deleta = 1d0/6d0
10423 c lagrange 3-pt.
10424  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
10425  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48

10430  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
10431  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
10432  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
10433  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
10434  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
10435  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
10436  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
10437  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
10438  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
10439  xsctca = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
10440  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
10441  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
10442  return
10443  end

11316 
11317  dleta = dlog10(eta)
11318  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
11319  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
11320  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
11321  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
11322  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
11323  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
11324  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
11325 c interpolating between the appropriate points
11326  delxi = 1d0/6d0
11327  deleta = 1d0/6d0
11328 c lagrange 3-pt.
11329  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
11330  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
11331  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
11332  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
11333  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
11334  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
11335  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
11336  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
11337  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
11338  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
11339  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
11340  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
11341  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
11342  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
11343  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
11344  xsctcf = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
11345  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
11346  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
11347  return
11348  end

12219  dleta = dlog10(eta)
12220  dlxi = dlog10(xi)
12221  if (dlxi .le. dlaxi(1)) dlxi = dlaxi(1)
12222  if (dlxi .ge. dlaxi(nxi)) dlxi = dlaxi(nxi)
12223  if (dleta .ge. dlaeta(neta)) dleta = dlaeta(neta)
12224  if (dleta .le. dlaeta(1)) dleta = dlaeta(1)
12225  call locate_nr(dlaeta,neta, dleta, ieta)
12226  call locate_nr(dlaxi, nxi, dlxi, ixi)
12227 c interpolating between the appropriate points
12228  delxi = 1d0/6d0
12229  deleta = 1d0/6d0
12230 c lagrange 3-pt.
12231  if (ixi .le. 2) ixi = 2
12232  if (ixi .ge. 48) ixi = 48
12233  if (ieta .le. 2) ieta = 2
12234  if (ieta .ge. 72) ieta = 72
12235  pxi = (dlxi - dlaxi(ixi))/delxi
12236  f(-1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi-1) +
12237  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi) +
12238  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta-1,ixi+1)
12239  f(0) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi-1) +
12240  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta,ixi) +
12241  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta,ixi+1)
12242  f(1) = pxi*(pxi-1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi-1) +
12243  1 (1d0 - pxi**2)*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi) +
12244  1 pxi*(pxi+1d0)/2d0*calcpts(ieta+1,ixi+1)
12245  peta = (dleta - dlaeta(ieta))/deleta
12246  xsdqtb = peta*(peta-1d0)/2d0*f(-1) +
12247  1 (1d0 - peta**2)*f(0) +
12248  1 peta*(peta+1d0)/2d0*f(1)
12249  return
12250  end
12251 c These are the functions that give the threshold dependence of the
12252 coefficient functions with the appropriate factors.
12253 c eta = (W^2 - 4d0*m2)/4d0/m2 where W is the CM energy of the gamma* parton
12254 c system. xi = mq2/m2 (Q^2/m2)
12255 c Longitudinal CF group structure: equation (13) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
12256  double precision function threshf_l(eta,xi)
12257  implicit none
12258 C=======================================================================
12259  double precision pi
12260  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
12261  double precision tr,cf,ca
12262  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
12263 C=======================================================================
12264  double precision eta, xi, beta, term1
12265  beta = dsqrt(eta/(1d0 + eta))
12266  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
12267  threshf_l = 1d0/6d0/pi*xi*term1**3*beta*beta*pi*pi/2d0
12268  return
12269  end
12270 c Transverse CF group structure: equation (14) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
12271  double precision function threshf_t(eta,xi)
12272  implicit none
12273 C=======================================================================
12274  double precision pi
12275  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
12276  double precision tr,cf,ca
12277  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
12278 C=======================================================================
12279  double precision eta, xi, beta, term1
12280  beta = dsqrt(eta/(1d0 + eta))
12281  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
12282  threshf_t = 0.25d0/pi*term1*pi*pi/2d0
12283  return
12284  end
12285 c Transverse CA group structure: equation (16) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
12286  double precision function thresha_t(eta,xi)
12287  implicit none
12288 C=======================================================================
12289  double precision pi
12290  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
12291  double precision tr,cf,ca
12292  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
12293 C=======================================================================
12294  double precision eta, xi, beta, term1
12295  beta = dsqrt(eta/(1d0 + eta))
12296  term1 = 1d0/(1d0 + 0.25d0*xi)
12297  thresha_t = 0.25d0/pi*term1*(beta*(dlog(8d0*beta*beta))**2
12298  1 - 5d0*beta*dlog(8d0*beta*beta) - 0.25d0*pi*pi)
12299  return
12300  end
12301 c Longitudinal CA group structure: equation (15) in PLB347 (1995) 143 - 151
12302  double precision function thresha_l(eta,xi)

12304 C=======================================================================

12337  double precision function threshbar_t(eta,xi)

12351 c---------------------------------
12352 c This gives the derivative of the transverse Born coefficient function
12353 c wrt to the mass as needed for the running MSbar mass
12354 c For QCD take TR = 1d0/2d0,
12355 c for QED take TR = 1d0
12356 c eta = (s - 4d0*m2)/4d0/m2, s is the gamma* gluon (gamma) CM Energy
12357 c xi = Q^2/m2
12358  double precision function dborn_t(eta,xi)
12359  implicit none
12360 C=======================================================================
12361  double precision pi
12362  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
12363  double precision tr,cf,ca
12364  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
12365 C=======================================================================
12366  double precision eta, xi
12367  double precision beta, lbeta
12368  beta = dsqrt(eta/(1d0+eta));
12369  lbeta = dlog((1d0+beta)/(1d0-beta))
12370  dborn_t = 2d0 * tr * pi * (1d0-beta**2) * xi *
12371  1 (-32d0*beta**3*lbeta + 32d0*beta**5*lbeta
12372  1 + xi**2*beta**6 - xi**2*beta**4 + 8d0*xi*beta**4
12373  1 - 64d0*beta**4 - xi**2*beta**2 - 16d0*xi*beta**2
12374  1 + 80d0*beta**2 + xi**2 + 8d0*xi + 16d0)*
12375  1 (-4-xi+xi*beta**2)**(-3)/beta
12376  return
12377  end
12378 c------------------------------------
12379 c mass derivative of Longitudinal coefficient function,
12380 c see above for additional comments
12381  double precision function dborn_l(eta,xi)
12382  implicit none
12383 C=======================================================================
12384  double precision pi
12385  parameter(pi=3.141592653589793d0)
12386  double precision tr,cf,ca
12387  parameter(tr=0.5d0,cf=4d0/3d0,ca=3d0)
12388 C=======================================================================
12389  double precision eta, xi
12390  double precision beta, lbeta
12391  beta = dsqrt(eta/(1d0+eta));
12392  lbeta = dlog((1d0+beta)/(1d0-beta))
12393  dborn_l = 32d0 * tr * pi * (1d0-beta**2)**3 * xi**2 *
12394  1 lbeta * (-4d0-xi+xi*beta**2)**(-3)
12395  return
12396  end
